listing_description:
The largest shopping mall in Bangladesh. This world class shopping center houses most of the major brands. You can find all kinds of consumer items starting from clothing, footwear, cosmetics, baby care products and electronics. Level 5 is fully dedicated to food and beverage joints. The area inside this mall is vast. There are ample numbers of escalators and elevators. Overall this is a very good place for shopping or just hanging out.
